      "4. SHADOW MODE: Check xsiam_socfw_ir_execution_raw \u2014 all C/E/R records must show execution_mode=shadow",
      "5. WARROOM ENTRIES: Verify [SHADOW] prefix on all Containment, Eradication, Recovery warroom entries",
